>https://education.github.com/discount_requests/application&lt;/a> 即可进入 GitHub Student Pack 教育优惠申请页面，如图&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://scau-jiwei.gitee.io/p/%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7github-student-pack%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E4%BC%98%E6%83%A0/img05.png"
