&lt;p>我们选择 “Student”，然后往下滚动，按照下图进行填写操作&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://scau-jiwei.gitee.io/p/%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7github-student-pack%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E4%BC%98%E6%83%A0/img06.png"
width="1688"
height="1665"
srcset="https://scau-jiwei.gitee.io/p/%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7github-student-pack%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E4%BC%98%E6%83%A0/img06_hua8a96b66149cd9a60e85f4b7d35eaae9_257598_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://scau-jiwei.gitee.io/p/%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7github-student-pack%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E4%BC%98%E6%83%A0/img06_hua8a96b66149cd9a60e85f4b7d35eaae9_257598_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
